OL,3,CSunderland youngster Chris Rigg
OL,4,Ccommits future to Black Cats
OL,6,FSunderland youngster Chris Rigg has
OL,7,Fcommited his future to the club after
OL,8,Fsigning his first professional
OL,9,Fcontract.
OL,11,FThe England Under-17 captain enjoyed a
OL,12,Fbreakout campaign last season, making
OL,13,F22 appearances and becoming
OL,14,FSunderland's youngest ever goalscorer.
