OL,3,CSunderland youngster Chris Rigg
OL,4,Ccommits future to Black Cats
OL,6,FThe 17-year-old contract was set to
OL,7,Fexpire over the summer and he was
OL,8,Flinked with a host of Premier League
OL,9,Fclubs, including fierce rivals
OL,10,FNewcastle United, but he has now put
OL,11,Fan end to the speculation by signing a
OL,12,Fnew three year deal.
OL,14,F"I am absolutely buzzing, to be
OL,15,Fhonest," he told the Sunderland club
OL,16,Fwebsite after the deal was agreed. "It
OL,17,Fis a proud moment for myself and my
OL,18,Ffamily to be signing my first
OL,19,Fprofessional contract at a club like
OL,20,FSunderland.
