OL,3,CSunderland youngster Chris Rigg
OL,4,Ccommits future to Black Cats
OL,6,F"I have been dying to sign it for
OL,7,Falmost a year now. I want to develop
OL,8,Fas a player and improve as a person `
OL,9,Fand I believe this is the best place
OL,10,Ffor me to do that.
OL,12,F"All the staff have been unbelievable
OL,13,Fwith me throughout my journey at the
OL,14,FAcademy of Light, but there are still
OL,15,Fso many improvements I can make. The
OL,16,Fhard work starts now, but I am looking
OL,17,Fforward to making many more memories
OL,18,Frepresenting this club."
