OL,3,CSunderland youngster Chris Rigg
OL,4,Ccommits future to Black Cats
OL,6,FThe news comes as another major boost
OL,7,Fto Sunderland following the recent
OL,8,Fappointment of new manager Regis Le
OL,9,FBris.
OL,11,F"I'm delighted for Chris, who has
OL,12,Falways communicated to us that
OL,13,FSunderland is where he wants to be,"
OL,14,FSporting Director Kristjaan Speakman
OL,15,Fsaid. "Chris' talent, and more
OL,16,Frecently his performances within the
OL,17,Ffirst team, made interest and
OL,18,Fspeculation inevitable, and it is a
OL,19,Ftestament to all behind the scenes
OL,20,Fthat he has committed his future to
OL,21,Four club."
